lowing this tutorial, you can fully automate Flutter mobile apps with AskUI. While this demo uses Flutter, the approach works for any Android app. AskUI‚Äôs visual automation removes fragile selectors, making mobile UI automation stable, adaptive, and AI-powered.</p><p id=\"><a href=\"https://www.askui.com/\">üëâ <strong id=\">Join AskUI Community to share your cases or get help.</strong></a></p>",
